features: ORIGIN: Made in Canada with domestic and imported materials.
Removable, adjustable hood with a shaped brim to stand up to winds.
Heavy-duty, rib-knit collar helps keep out the cold
Water-resistant Arctic-Tech fabric exterior for durability and weather-resistance
Quilt-through design for even heat distribution and bulk reduction
One interior pocket; security with zipper closure
FILL: 625 Fill Power White Duck Down
Arctic Tech Extreme conditions: Our most proven textile designed to stay dry in extreme conditions and climates.

Whether you're working up a sweat hiking trails, embarking on an urban adventure, or exploring the coldest places on Earth, we've developed the Thermal Experience Index (TEI) to help you find the right Canada Goose jacket for your body, your activities, and lifestyle.
Thermal Experience Index Rating: 3 (-10°C / -20°C): Fundamental warmth fashioned for everyday use.
